flowchart TB
    user((Internet User)) --> alb[Application Load Balancer
Public subnets across 2 AZs]
    alb --> tg[Target Group
HTTP health checks]
    tg --> ec2a[EC2 Web VM A
NGINX]
    tg --> ec2b[EC2 Web VM B
NGINX]
    asg[Auto Scaling Group
min=2 desired=2 max=3
self-healing replacement] -. manages .-> ec2a
    asg -. manages .-> ec2b
    lt[Launch Template
AMI + user-data] --> asg
    vpc[VPC: public subnets only
no NAT Gateway for low cost] --- alb
